    option     dump or config

version

sh4u <file>

Arguments:
    file       file to play

printf <text> <color> <bgcolor>

Arguments:
    text       text to display
    color      text color
    bgcolor    text background color

ggp <pkgname> <local?>

Arguments:
    pkgname    package name
    local?     optional local mode


